patternDescription: The main part of the rifle and the scope are coated with a glossy dark green paint. The buttstock and the handle are painted solid black. The magazine and several individual parts of the weapon are not painted.

name: UMP-45 | Fade
appearanceHistory: UMP-45 | Fade was added to the game on September 22, 2021, as part of The 2021 Dust 2 Collection, which was released alongside the start of Operation Riptide.
patternDescription: The body of this SMG is chromed and coated with translucent paints creating gradient transitions. The skin’s color scheme comprises various shades of purple, pink, and yellow. Individual parts of the weapon remain unpainted. The gradient’s color ratio depends on the pattern index.

name: MAC-10 | Stalker
appearanceHistory: MAC-10 | Stalker was added to the game on November 18, 2019, as part of The Shattered Web Collection, which was released alongside the start of Operation Shattered Web. The skin was created by OniLolz, Zaphk, and 2Minds.
patternDescription: The body of the submachine gun is painted yellow and complemented by an animalistic pattern of diagonal stripes and different-sized spots. The color scheme of the pattern includes black, white, blue and various shades of brown. The main element of the skin is an image of a wild cat’s head made in blue and pink. The design is complemented by a black-and-pink inscription “Stalker” located above the trigger. The magazine is adorned with blue diagonal stripes, the belt is made in yellow.

name: MP7 | Olive Plaid
appearanceHistory: MP7 | Olive Plaid was added to the game on July 1, 2014, as part of The Baggage Collection, which was released alongside the start of Operation Breakout.
patternDescription: The body of the submachine gun is adorned with a tartan pattern painted in olive and beige colors. Individual parts of the weapon are painted in various shades of olive color.

name: MP9 | Wild Lily
appearanceHistory: MP9 | Wild Lily was added to the game on November 18, 2019, as part of The St. Marc Collection, which was released alongside the start of Operation Shattered Web.
patternDescription: The black-and-gray body of the submachine gun is adorned with images of white lilies and banana leaves and complemented by accents in the form of white and pink lines. The color scheme of the pattern uses various shades of blue, purple and pink.

name: MP5-SD | Autumn Twilly
appearanceHistory: MP5-SD | Autumn Twilly was added to the game on September 22, 2021, as part of The 2021 Train Collection, which was released alongside the start of Operation Riptide.
patternDescription: The body of this SMG has been painted with an abstract pattern of numerous graphic elements. The skin's color scheme comprises various shades of brown and beige. The handle is painted solid black. The buttstock is coated with a red-brown semi-gloss paint.

name: M249 | Emerald Poison Dart
appearanceHistory: M249 | Emerald Poison Dart was added to the game on March 15, 2017, as part of The Spectrum Collection, which was released alongside the “Take a trip to the Canals” update. The skin was created by PTP.
patternDescription: The entire body of the machine gun is adorned with an animalistic pattern of different-sized stripes and spots. The pattern imitates the color of the Emerald poison frog. The color scheme of the skin includes black and various shades of yellow and teal. The rear sight, the barrel and individual parts of the body are not painted.

name: Negev | Mjölnir
appearanceHistory: Negev | Mjölnir was added to the game on November 18, 2019, as part of The Norse Collection, which was released alongside the start of Operation Shattered Web.
patternDescription: The skin is named after Thor's hammer. The body of the machine gun is engraved with ethnic Old Norse ornaments and painted with metallic paint in various shades of red and orange. Individual parts of the weapon are made in black. The handguard is made of wood and adorned with carvings.
